caller_intent: Navanda Harris wanted to make a payment for her auto insurance policy.
resolution_steps: Agent confirmed Navanda's identity and accessed her policy details.
Agent verified the payment amount ($126.81) and confirmed credit card details (ending in 6986).
Agent processed the payment through the Auto Owners system.
Agent informed Navanda that a confirmation email would be sent upon successful processing.
summary: Navanda Harris contacted Auto Insurance to pay her auto policy. The agent processed a $126.81 payment via credit card and confirmed the transaction would be emailed. Navanda did not require further assistance.
